welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Progress Village, where southern charm meets modern progress! Get ready to experience our vibrant community and discover why we're known for our friendly locals, delicious food, and rich history. Enjoy your stay and let us show you all that Progress Village has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Peter O'Knight Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Peter O'Knight Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tampa International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Airside A
terminals.description: Airside A at Tampa International Airport is primarily used for domestic flights by Delta and American Airlines.

terminals.name: Airside C
terminals.description: Airside C at Tampa International Airport serves domestic flights by Southwest Airlines.

terminals.name: Airside E
terminals.description: Airside E at Tampa International Airport is used for international flights, as well as some domestic flights by United and Spirit Airlines.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Whitted Airport houses the ticket counters, baggage claim, and security checkpoints.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Whitted Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal handles all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Airside Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is used for flights to and from Canada and the Caribbean.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Zephyrhills Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Zephyrhills Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
